organizations.name: johor dap more  federal territory bn youth

text:
More 
Federal Territory BN Youth's plan to give out free petrol has exposed the ruling party's insincerity, as they were responsible for raising fuel prices, said a DAP leader. 
Johor DAP chief Liew Chin Tong said Pakatan Harapan should take heart that BN had “copied” their idea of helping the needy by giving out free petrol out of the representatives' own pockets.
